snippet.title: Surveillance Tape Shows Amber Heard Cozying Up to Elon Musk in Johnny Depp's Private Elevator
snippet.description:
Surveillance Tape Shows Amber Heard Cozying Up to Elon Musk in Johnny Depp's Private Elevator..
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChjDtGelMNkllI5S22oO_aA?sub_confirmation=1
 Screenshots from the surveillance footage appear to corroborate the 'Alice in Wonderland' star's claim that the 'Aquaman' actress started an affair with the Tesla mogul one month into their marriage.   Mar 28, 2020   AceShowbiz - New photos have surfaced showing Amber Heard cuddling up to Elon Musk in a private elevator to Johnny Depp's private penthouse. The images, which are taken from surveillance tape inside the elevator, see a bikini-clad Amber with the Tesla mogul's arm being draped around her as they rode the elevator at the luxury downtown L.A. apartment where she once lived with Johnny.    At one point, the 33-year-old actress, who wore what appeared to be a towel over her bikini, leaned forward and rested her head on Elon's chest. According to Daily Mail which obtained the photos, there are no clues as to when the images were taken, but the site notes that security guards have previously stated that the SpaceX CEO visited the actress on multiple occasions before and after sh ...
